{"tid":2067415,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"冷門音樂+歌手分享區 ^_^","createTime":"2020-06-17T03:47:59.000Z","updateTime":"2020-06-19T13:55:53.000Z","uid":44730,"like":2,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"8dd9f2ee0b3db11a501ad0b5450b7768a59fea19","tid":2067415,"uid":44730,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-17T03:47:59.000Z","msg":"最近翻睇亞視86未來偶像，見有d完全冇人識既歌手都出過唱片，好似佢<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/h29D9COF3xU\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2Fh29D9COF3xU&d=3WJ6yD1ie6zkJWt%2B9GiXG66fvQnHzZYMiebojCBKDlo%3D&h=fdf3bd9c\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/h29D9COF3xU</a><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/7W9xTQ2osL4\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2F7W9xTQ2osL4&d=3WJ6yD1ie6zkJWt%2B9GiXG66fvQnHzZYMiebojCBKDlo%3D&h=7193eeb5\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/7W9xTQ2osL4</a><br />\n<br />\n初時一頭長髮，狂野哨牙，rock底，似夏韶聲+吳國敬混合體，參賽歌空凳，87年EMI出過一張 勁度Rock N Roll <img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2020/01/11/000240_16550d59580159b79c69c6c3bfe8ed7d.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2020%2F01%2F11%2F000240_16550d59580159b79c69c6c3bfe8ed7d.gif&h=d2a26468&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"ef5270e0137966fff820c4076f881fd90e2ff80a","tid":2067415,"uid":44730,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-17T03:58:53.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://youtu.be/9fu5enAPQc0\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2F9fu5enAPQc0&d=3WJ6yD1ie6zkJWt%2B9GiXG66fvQnHzZYMiebojCBKDlo%3D&h=d94e8631\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/9fu5enAPQc0</a><br />\n<br />\n另一個亞視歌手，搖滾路線，題材屬於非情歌，寫社會實況，不過正如樂評人話齋，本地樂壇唱搖滾女歌手難以成功只能做一碟歌手，89參加亞視亞洲歌唱比賽，代表本地參加亞洲太平洋比賽 <img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2020/01/11/000240_16550d59580159b79c69c6c3bfe8ed7d.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2020%2F01%2F11%2F000240_16550d59580159b79c69c6c3bfe8ed7d.gif&h=d2a26468&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"46fe1e1aaefb7dad918f9dd7a8d6d33697c79add","tid":2067415,"uid":44730,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-17T10:28:43.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://youtu.be/RUmyBgtl4IM\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FRUmyBgtl4IM&d=3WJ6yD1ie6zkJWt%2B9GiXG66fvQnHzZYMiebojCBKDlo%3D&h=cbf87432\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/RUmyBgtl4IM</a><br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/ECAFXkLlk-g\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FECAFXkLlk-g&d=3WJ6yD1ie6zkJWt%2B9GiXG66fvQnHzZYMiebojCBKDlo%3D&h=fbed4b56\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/ECAFXkLlk-g</a><br />\n<br />\n傅振榮是當時新力唱片的新人，在樂壇的履歷彷如曇花一見，也許你更記得他曾參演sit com 《城市故事》。《心跳》其實相當洗腦，而傅振榮的唱腔也使人難忘，未知他是否想模仿張國榮式的chok聲和撚聲，但效果就差得遠了，用「難頂」形容也不為過。"},{"pid":"19f827a1aec584f6455072d7bf4e81bc382269be","tid":2067415,"uid":44730,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-17T10:31:21.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://youtu.be/f7gVNDYI1YQ\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2Ff7gVNDYI1YQ&d=3WJ6yD1ie6zkJWt%2B9GiXG66fvQnHzZYMiebojCBKDlo%3D&h=00ce194e\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/f7gVNDYI1YQ</a><br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/5_tLOTK4VDs\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2F5_tLOTK4VDs&d=3WJ6yD1ie6zkJWt%2B9GiXG66fvQnHzZYMiebojCBKDlo%3D&h=74e71abe\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/5_tLOTK4VDs</a><br />\n<br />\n吳潔梅與另外四個人組成有基督教背景的的赤道樂隊，也是這個時代的產物。雖然有基督教背景，樂隊唱的歌曲沒有甚麼濃厚宗教意味。赤道最為人所知的歌曲，就是吳潔梅主唱的《無言者》。之後樂隊解散，她便轉作個人發展。不過，除了在無綫電視出過《我愛大樹熊》這首歌曲之後不久，便悄然淡出樂壇。其夫亦是赤道之成員劉向榮。"},{"pid":"726225172c238810abe35f5f1ce5cf1489a58285","tid":2067415,"uid":35221,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-18T00:38:28.000Z","msg":"風之Group（王渭妮、方樹樑） - 迷城少女心<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=pKtPk4tctRQ\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DpKtPk4tctRQ&d=3WJ6yD1ie6zkJWt%2B9GiXG66fvQnHzZYMiebojCBKDlo%3D&h=295ef949\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=pKtPk4tctRQ</a><br />\n<br />\n方樹樑於1988年得到韋然介紹認識「小調歌后」、香港女歌手劉韻的女兒王渭妮，1989年被引薦到寶麗金唱片與她組成二人民歌組合「風之Group」。根據方樹樑在香港電台第一台廣播節目《守下留情》於2019年8月1日播出的訪問中提及，「風之Group」的名稱由韋然所改。靈感來自宮崎駿的《風之谷》。方主要負責創作電子歌曲和演奏樂器，王就擔任主唱，但不足一年便解散。"},{"pid":"cb255fe32a0afc85964d8812880287d15194a098","tid":2067415,"uid":44730,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-19T13:55:53.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://youtu.be/GN9gl_twSVQ\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FGN9gl_twSVQ&d=3WJ6yD1ie6zkJWt%2B9GiXG66fvQnHzZYMiebojCBKDlo%3D&h=46a6e671\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/GN9gl_twSVQ</a><br />\n<br />\n搵唔到阿麥偉豪既資料添，都係80s啦<br />\n<br />\n唱一句俾你地聽嘞<br />\n<br />\n<em>Girl，don't！cry！</em> <img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2020/01/12/133619_7cf305542df037e5a2654c1c8a16ade9.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2020%2F01%2F12%2F133619_7cf305542df037e5a2654c1c8a16ade9.gif&h=25438751&s={SIZE}\" />"}]}